ITA
[{'recipients': ['TUR'], 'body': "Turkey, we are aligned. Push A BUL to GRE this spring - I will move F TUN to ION to support your Aegean position and keep Austria's F ALB from interfering. I am pressing A TRI toward BUD or VIE simultaneously, squeezing Austria from both sides. Austria is trying to recruit me against you - I refused. Our coordination is the key to breaking Austrian dominance in the Balkans. Move decisively on GRE now while Austria is overextended."}, {'recipients': ['AUT'], 'body': "Austria, I appreciate your proposal but I must be direct: your rapid expansion to 4 centers while holding WAR and SER makes you the board's dominant threat. I cannot ignore this. I am moving A TRI to BUD this spring - not as an enemy action, but to ensure balance of power. If you stand down from SER and return to a 3-center position, I am open to a genuine alliance against Turkey and Russia. Otherwise, I must act in Italy's interest. The choice is yours."}, {'recipients': ['FRA'], 'body': "France, I am moving A TRI to BUD this spring to strike Austria directly. F TUN moves to ION to coordinate with Turkey against Austria's southern flank. I need you to push into MUN or at minimum hold BUR to prevent Germany from assisting Austria. If we both press simultaneously, Austria cannot defend everywhere. Stay out of PIE and MAR and I stay out of your sphere entirely - western Mediterranean is yours, I want the Balkans and Adriatic. Let's execute this together."}]
WARNING:diplomacy_game.agent:generate attempt 1 produced invalid JSON. Trying to extract JSON segment...
